descriptionHtml:
Well, this file was completely for my own use, but letiger42 asked me to upload it, so here you go!

The file\'s a vampire - again, this was intended for my own use - so you can cure her pretty easily by going to Morthal or just using console. She\'s fairly low level, so you can raise her up to specialize in whatever you want. 

To upload, place the file in the saved games folder.

Enjoy! :3
author: Diana
